summary: Adds two new spells to the game: Conjure Dwarven Centurion, and Conjure Giant Dwarven Centurion.
descriptionHtml:
This mod will implement a brand new dungeon where the Dovahkiin must test his combat ability in the greatest battle yet. 

The mighty hero will be greatly rewarded... If he makes it out alive.

The Secret Dwarven Chamber is located in the Norther Part of Skyrim, to the East of Ustengrav. 

Bring your potions ;)
author: noneo
